  "description": "A scenic coastal view features a sandy beach in the foreground meeting the breaking waves of a blue ocean. The water appears choppy with a visible swell, and white foam crests the waves as they roll towards the shore. In the distance, a hazy landmass, likely an island or coastline, is visible on the horizon under a partly cloudy sky. The sky is a mix of blue and white with puffy clouds. The beach itself is a dark, almost grey-brown color, textured with footprints and patterns created by the receding water. The overall impression is one of a remote, natural environment.",
